This paper is likely to belong to the Information Retrieval (cs.IR) sub-category as it deals with the problem of product recommendation, which is a common application of information retrieval. Additionally, the paper also incorporates ideas from sentiment analysis (cs.CL), multi-relational learning (cs.LG), and machine learning (cs.AI), which are all relevant to the field of information retrieval. The paper also involves the use of embeddings, which are commonly used in database systems (cs.DB).
